{
  "texts": [
    "Resizable-ViT efficiently processes images of varied resolutions while doing well on image recognition tasks by dynamically adapting to input sizes.",
    "All of these variants have been shown to enhance the performance and efficiency of Vision Transformers and have been applied to a variety of tasks, including image recognition, object detection, and medical imaging, with SOTA results.",
    "Vision Transformer (ViT) has attracted great interest in computer vision duties due to its capacity to process images with high precision and efficiency.",
    "Recent developments and applications have been made to the ViT architecture.",
    "The DeiT model, which enhances the training of ViT models using data augmentation and distillation techniques, is one of the most significant innovations."
  ]
}